Name: Delicious Grainfruit Chips
Desc: Crispy triangular chips. Crunch-crunch-crunch go the crispy pieces! You simply cannot stop pairing it with the sweet and sour sauce, the rich, fragrant cheese, the delicious shredded meat... Why does this combination have to. Be. So. Delicious?
Effect: Restores 22% of Max HP to the selected character and regenerates 470 HP every 5s for 30s.
